Specifically derived from llama.cpp:

  - shaders/iq_tables.glsl
      Quantization lookup tables generated from
      ggml/src/ggml-common.h.

  - shaders/metal/gemv_iq4_xs.metal
    shaders/metal/gemv_q6_k.metal
    shaders/metal/gemv_iq3_xxs.metal
      Adopt the llama.cpp Metal kernel work shape (threads-per-row and
      per-lane block assignment). The dequantization and accumulation
      code is original to this project.

  - The GGUF container format and its quantization block layouts
      (Q4_0, Q8_0, Q6_K, IQ4_XS, IQ3_XXS) as defined by ggml.

Correctness throughout this project is defined as token-for-token agreement
with llama.cpp on identical input token IDs; llama.cpp is used as the
reference implementation for all parity testing.

